{"tid":1673252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今咩世只嫁前線巴？無可能！ 點解要我香港同自由取其一？","createTime":"2019-10-24T14:13:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T12:58:07.000Z","uid":66390,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"82457841a9a03c3ec6cf6db6c2359cde064ec7ae","tid":1673252,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T14:13:53.000Z","msg":"我同我女朋友兩年啦<br />\n佢唔想再過提心吊膽既生活<br />\n分左手<br />\n<br />\n我又知自己只會愈來愈癲<br />\n見到差佬 愈來愈失控<br />\n唔係死 就被捕<br />\n<br />\n係咁諗 到底為左香港 值唔值咁做<br />\n但當你連自己前途都唔知 憑咩同人講未來<br />\n人地諗到未來 都會開始懷疑<br />\n<br />\n所以「今世只嫁前線巴」係扼尻人<br />\n係大家未諗得深<br />\n<br />\n但當我㨂愛情<br />\n我見到手足被打被捕<br />\n我又點忍？<br />\n<br />\n到底愛情同自由<br />\n邊一個價更高<br />\n<br />\n我真係好撚亂 好辛苦<br />\n身邊已經有3個前線巴都係因為咁分左手<br />\n<br />\n最後個相擁 大家係咁喊 大家都唔肯放手<br />\n真係好難受 <br />\n<br />\n我愛你<br />\n<br />\n可能我會追返你 <br />\n可能我會就咁算<br />\n我都唔知..."},{"pid":"b11617f5acc5043c105503fa319f32ddd60e9699","tid":1673252,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T14:14:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gv2xOLu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgv2xOLu.jpg&h=a9eb1a8f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"97d0848fba75ad6fb733b7a32ba230918f65ae81","tid":1673252,"uid":66390,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b11617f5acc5043c105503fa319f32ddd60e9699","tid":1673252,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T14:14:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gv2xOLu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgv2xOLu.jpg&h=a9eb1a8f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T14:15:30.000Z","msg":"屌你呀 分左手呀"},{"pid":"27b6f67165acd22566f8b9f2150f568893838a57","tid":1673252,"uid":149487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T14:15:53.000Z","msg":"作為絲 只可以講加油"},{"pid":"2c8d7df7fbcdc91daa701646cd772e6e1ebbf18e","tid":1673252,"uid":31